      biz.sudden.designCoordination.collaborativePlanning.domain.CP_Actor

public class CP_Actor
extends NegotiationIssue

In the context of "CollaborativePlanning", Actor acts as an NegotiationIssue and further as CommunicationItem, so that it is possible to talk about Actors. Due to the fact that "Actor" is a base domain objects, this actor should only act as an adapter for the "Actor" which resides in "baseAndUtility"
